# Runtime bundle source files are byte-strict. Git's default
# `text=auto` line-ending conversion CRLF-corrupts files like
# `runtime-smoke-imports.txt` whose canonical byte format requires
# LF-only line endings (correction #63). Force LF on every file
# under this tree to guarantee Windows-hosted CI checkouts see the
# same bytes the builder enforces.
* text eol=lf
*.zip binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.ico binary
